About Conscient Heritage Max

Heritage Max located Sector 102 , Gurgaon has amazing luxury flats available from INR 1.05 Cr to 1.72 Cr.. Promoting the unique concept of live more every day, picking a new game every time and pushing your limits, the Heritage Max Sector 102 is a sports lifestyle residential society that is surrounded by 90% open areas.  The ready to move- in society consists of 6 towers and 493 residential apartments. These 3BHK and 4BHK residential apartments vary in the size range of 1870 sq.ft. to 2860 sq.ft. The society is accepted for home loans by well-known banks like HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, Punjab National Bank, State Bank of India, etc.

Project detail
Allowing you to explore more every day and learn a lot more about the potential that you have, the Heritage Max in Gurgaon offers you both, superior living standards and healthy living. At Heritage Max, you actually get to enjoy the world- class sports amenities within the boundaries of the society and can always enjoy the privilege of being a sportsman.
Sports activities like cycling track, floodlit football field, tennis court, garden court, basketball court, squash court, table tennis, etc. are available.
Stay fit with gym and jogging track.
Kids can play and socialize with their friends in kids play area.

The Heritage Max is constructed by the Conscient Infrastructure Pvt. Ltd. that has been delivering world- class residential spaces in India by understanding the needs of a modern customer. At Magicbricks, you can explore Heritage Max construction update, Heritage Max reviews, Heritage Max price list, floor plan, photos and a lot more.
Keeping you connected to all the prime areas, the Heritage Max offers easy accessibility to NH- 8, Dwarka Expressway, DPS, Indus Valley Public School, DAV Public School, ESI Hospital, Sector 101, 100 and 99, Greenwood Public School, Blue Bells Public School, Euro International School, Green Field Public School, ESIC Hospital, Sanjeevani Hospital, Sri Balaji Hospital, Alfaa Health Care, Sagar Hospital, Numbardar Market, Good Luck Public School, Lord Jesus Preparatory School, Gyan Devi Montessori School, etc.

The beautiful Conscient Heritage Max's commencement certificate has been granted. The project's occupancy certificate not granted. Conscient Heritage Max is a high-quality yet affordable residential project by Conscient Infrastructure Pvt. Ltd. . The complete address of the site is Dwarka Expy, Sector 102, Gurugram, Haryana 122505. The project is located at one of the most sought after pin codes that is 122006.
